entries.femaleVariant: Pierced it. We're in.
Definitely not your ordinary van.
Jam-packed with hardware, my optics don't see any manufacturer info or detect any mods…
We are about to find out.
They don't mass produce trucks like those. What are they doing, what are they hiding?
entries.maleVariant: They don't mass produce trucks like those. What're they doin', what're they hiding?

entries.femaleVariant: Earjacking? Huh, could be the security firm or government. Media scouting for dirt on the Peralezes?
Whoever it is, our intruder could be in there. Think it's time I went and said hello...
entries.maleVariant: Well, whoever it is, our intruder could be in there. Think it's time I went and said hello...

entries.femaleVariant: Brain scans, the Peralezes'. Biological casts, neuroplasticity…
Fuck... What about that? The blue shit.
Fresh neural links. They're not spying on them, Johnny, they're fuckin' with their heads!
entries.maleVariant: Fresh neural links. They're not spyin' on them, Johnny, they're fuckin' with their heads!

entries.femaleVariant: So, what're we lookin' at?
They're plantin' new memories in their heads, modifying their personalities... This is big shit, Johnny.
Fuck me…
Shit, they're wipin' the data... Ugh, we been made!
entries.maleVariant: Shit, they're wipin' the data... We been made.

entries.femaleVariant: Quick, download the data. Whoever comes lookin' for it – that's your suspect.
Now they know someone's been in their database.
Gonna lose 'em if you don't pick up the pace!
Shit, must've spotted me!
Strange gear... same kind we found back in that secret room.
Shame it got fried to oblivion.
Quick, don't lose 'em!
Pictures, medical records... vulnerability to neuroplasticity? Huh, it's some kinda database.
entries.maleVariant: Pictures, medical records... vulnerability to neuroplasticity? It's some kinda database.

entries.femaleVariant: Mean to say someone's literally controlling our upstanding politicians' minds?
Got other guinea pigs besides the Peralezes, too.
Wonder if they also know WHO…
Couldn't ask the NCPD for better records than this.
Uh-huh. Red blots are memory residue in the hippocampus region. See how they're bleeding into the blue?
entries.maleVariant: Mhm. Red blots are memory residue in the hippocampus region. See how they're bleedin' into the blue?

entries.femaleVariant: [Jack in]
How 'bout we take the wheels, V? That van could give us the slip any second.
There! That's the bitch! Zero her!
entries.maleVariant: There! That's the cocksucker! Zero him!

entries.femaleVariant: Don't lose 'em, V!
You look at politicians and see a curated display. But behind the scenes it's all-out war.
Got the slimy cocksucker! C'mon, let's see what's inside.
Oh, now you're interested?
We could expose a corpo conspiracy here, V, I'm tellin' ya.
They could be corpo spies or who the fuck knows what.
Citizens don't choose their representatives...
Then who?
The key players. String-pullers. They spy on all the Peralezes, look for weak spots, blackmail, rig elections...
Shit... they're taking us into Northside? This can't end well, Johnny...
[Disconnect]
Sons of bitches…
